org.jnosql.artemis.document

Class AbstractDocumentTemplate

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jnosql.artemis.document.AbstractDocumentTemplate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DocumentTemplate

    public abstract class AbstractDocumentTemplate
extends Object
implements DocumentTemplate
    This class provides a skeletal implementation of the DocumentTemplate interface, to minimize the effort required to implement this interface.
